673:     // Note: configured decoder filters are appended to decoder_filters_.
674:     // This means that if filters are configured in the following order (assume all three filters
675:     // are both decoder/encoder filters):
676:     //   http_filters:
677:     //     - A
678:     //     - B
679:     //     - C
